title: "Space Oddity"
description: Singer Amanda Palmer pays tribute to the inimitable David Bowie with a cover of "Space Oddity." She's joined onstage by Jherek Bischoff, TED Fellow Usman Riaz and, no, your eyes are not deceiving you, none other than former Vice President Al Gore.
author: Amanda Palmer, Jherek Bischoff, Usman Riaz
keywords: TED, talks, live music, music, performance, singer, vocals, guitar, TED Fellows, entertainment
